org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.parquet.vector

Class BaseVectorizedColumnReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.parquet.vector.BaseVectorizedColumnReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VectorizedColumnReader
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VectorizedDummyColumnReader, VectorizedListColumnReader, VectorizedPrimitiveColumnReader

    public abstract class BaseVectorizedColumnReader
extends Object
implements VectorizedColumnReader
    It's column level Parquet reader which is used to read a batch of records for a column, part of the code is referred from Apache Spark and Apache Parquet.
